Step A: Sirf Password badalna ho
Command: node scripts/createAdmin.js <aapka_email> <naya_password>

Example: node scripts/createAdmin.js admin@test.com myNewPass789

Step B: Sirf Email badalna ho
Command: node scripts/createAdmin.js <purana_email> null <naya_email>

Example: node scripts/createAdmin.js old@test.com null new@test.com

(Beech mein null likhne ka matlab hai ki password wahi purana rahe).

Step C: Dono badalna ho (Email + Password)
Command: node scripts/createAdmin.js <purana_email> <naya_password> <naya_email>

Example: node scripts/createAdmin.js old@test.com pass123 new@test.com

Step D: Naya Admin banana ho
Command: node scripts/createAdmin.js <naya_email> <password>

Example: node scripts/createAdmin.js fresh@test.com welcome123